cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text classification. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves learning and optimization techniques. Additionally, it could be relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as text is often a component of image analysis tasks, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves neural network models.
